Thompson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 293}, {\"ngram\": \"the end day\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"the ages\", \"from\": 382, \"to\": 390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brit produced a huge personal best of 14.44m in the shot put, as well as her best high jump performance in five years, to lead on 4055 points after four events, 48 clear of defending champion and long-time rival Nafi Thiam.\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 610, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"score\": 0.9382360940984357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nafi\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nafi_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Brit\", \"from\": 394, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"14.44m\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 442}, {\"ngram\": \"the shot put\", \"from\": 446, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"her best high jump performance\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"five years\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 515}, {\"ngram\": \"4055 points\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 539}, {\"ngram\": \"four events\", \"from\": 546, \"to\": 557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson put years of injury woe behind her to regain her world title in Budapest last year, but is still searching for a first ever Olympic medal at what is her fourth Games.\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 704, \"end\": 712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.6848240854202635, \"rank\": 0.4602290149157319, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 623, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 644, \"to\": 649}, {\"ngram\": \"injury woe\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 663}, {\"ngram\": \"her world title\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 700}, {\"ngram\": \"a first ever Olympic medal\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 777}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourth Games\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Having made her debut at London 2012 as a teenager alongside Jessica Ennis-Hill, she was well-fancied to make the podium in Rio four years later, but could only finish sixth, before pulling her calf during the 200m in Tokyo and being forced out of the competition.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 832, \"end\": 843, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999968354132, \"rank\": 3.1636784247897215e-09, \"text\": \"London 2012\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2012_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 868, \"end\": 886, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jessica Ennis-Hill\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Ennis-Hill\"}, {\"begin\": 931, \"end\": 934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999997999112, \"rank\": 2.0031523078973636e-10, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9972695238581806, \"rank\": 0.002737668746041647, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her debut\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenager\", \"from\": 847, \"to\": 857}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium\", \"from\": 917, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"her calf\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1005}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1021}, {\"ngram\": \"the competition\", \"from\": 1055, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 31-year-old's build-up to Paris has also been far from smooth.She pulled out of the European Championships in Romeafter three events because of injury and has not completed a full heptathlon in 2024 as she continues to manage an Achilles issue.\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999949978, \"rank\": 5.104601686166575e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1161, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.810473381551333e-26, \"text\": \"European Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/European_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 1306, \"end\": 1314, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 0.9999999939059308, \"rank\": 6.094107262623962e-09, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 31-year-old's build-up\", \"from\": 1073, \"to\": 1099}, {\"ngram\": \"Romeafter\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1196}, {\"ngram\": \"three events\", \"from\": 1197, \"to\": 1209}, {\"ngram\": \"injury\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"a full heptathlon\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1267}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If her fitness remained a question-mark at the start of Thursday, though, by nightfall the script had flipped: it appears the world champion might just be in some of the best shape of her life.\", \"from\": 1323, \"to\": 1516, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her fitness\", \"from\": 1326, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"a question-mark\", \"from\": 1347, \"to\": 1362}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 1366, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1387}, {\"ngram\": \"nightfall\", \"from\": 1400, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"the script\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1420}, {\"ngram\": \"the world champion\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1463}, {\"ngram\": \"the best shape\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1515}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson began the morning running a season's best time of 13.40seconds in the 100m hurdles - a tenth-of-a-second quicker than she had opened when winning world gold in Budapest 12 months ago - before clearing 1.92m in the high jump for the first time since her maiden World Championship success, at Doha 2019.\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1695, \"end\": 1703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.6848240854202635, \"rank\": 0.4602290149157319, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 1518, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"a season's best time\", \"from\": 1561, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m hurdles\", \"from\": 1601, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"a-second\", \"from\": 1631, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"world gold\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1691}, {\"ngram\": \"1.92m\", \"from\": 1736, \"to\": 1741}, {\"ngram\": \"the high jump\", \"from\": 1745, \"to\": 1758}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1777}, {\"ngram\": \"her maiden World Championship success\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1821}, {\"ngram\": \"Doha\", \"from\": 1826, \"to\": 1830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The evening session began with what is traditionally one of the Liverpudlian's weakest events, the shot put, and at one stage she looked set to surrender a swing of well over 100 points to Thiam, after the Belgian - a much stronger thrower - equalled her personal best of 15.54m.\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 2117, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1902, \"end\": 1914, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"score\": 0.9999996482316128, \"rank\": 3.5176843085549566e-07, \"text\": \"Liverpudlian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool\"}, {\"begin\": 2044, \"end\": 2051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9727535503213501, \"rank\": 0.018754912265639554, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The evening session\", \"from\": 1838, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"the shot\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 1941}, {\"ngram\": \"one stage\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"a swing\", \"from\": 1992, \"to\": 1999}, {\"ngram\": \"well over 100 points\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2023}, {\"ngram\": \"Thiam\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"15.54m.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Johnson-Thompson, by contrast, had managed only 13.38m across the first two rounds and never in her life thrown beyond the 14-metre line.\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Johnson-Thompson\", \"from\": 2119, \"to\": 2135}, {\"ngram\": \"contrast\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"only 13.38m\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"the first two rounds\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2201}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"the 14-metre line\", \"from\": 2238, \"to\": 2255}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her third and final attempt, though, she launched past it and then some, her mark of 14.44m adding more than half-a-metre to her lifetime best.\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2405, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her third and final attempt\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2289}, {\"ngram\": \"her mark\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"more than half-a-metre\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"her lifetime\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2399}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That meant Thiam carrying a lead of 50 points into the final event of the day, the 200m.\", \"from\": 2407, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Thiam\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"a lead\", \"from\": 2433, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"50 points\", \"from\": 2443, \"to\": 2452}, {\"ngram\": \"the final event\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Johnson-Thompson's 23.44 was a second quicker than her rivals to effectively flip that margin, with the long jump, javelin and 800m to come.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that margin\", \"from\": 2587, \"to\": 2598}, {\"ngram\": \"the long jump\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2618}, {\"ngram\": \"javelin\", \"from\": 2620, \"to\": 2627}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MORE ABOUT Have your say... 1 Crime Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line train after youths told to stop vaping by middle-aged passenger Fight breaks out on Elizabeth line after youths told to stop vaping 2 Football Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup, confirmed team news, injury latest for Premier League today Liverpool XI vs Brighton: Starting lineup and c